data.description: Welcome home to this 5 bedroom Eagle River beauty!  The fully remodeled kitchen is a show stopper with it's high end hickory cabinets, stainless Viking appliances, built in grill, under cab lighting, and gorgeous quartz counters. 3 bedrooms (including the primary with an en suite bathroom and walk in closet) and full hall bath upstairs. 2 bedrooms and a full bath downstairs. (See Supplement)Both hall baths have been completely updated with slate tile shower surrounds and thoughtful finishes. There are 2 family rooms, both with fireplaces. The outdoor space boasts ample, paved parking, plus RV pad and large shed with overhead door for additional storage. Fully fenced yard and spacious teakwood deck. All this, nestled in the heart of Eagle River.
